name: Exuberance No. 1 Radiant Magenta
description:
Exuberance No. 1 Radiant Magenta catalyzes cosmic kinetic energy.
Exuberance No. 1 Radiant Magenta is a one-of-a-kind artistic collaboration that intertwines Tery Spataro's flower photographs and the artificial intelligence of Playform.io to give life to this transfixing new creation. The Exuberance art series are physical surface designs.
